      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index RH = NIH_device / NIH_predicate is the regulatory acceptance criterion. CFD computes scalar stress-based hemolysis power law integrated along Lagrangian particle trajectories, directly yielding NIH. QoI is mechanistically linked to red blood cell damage in clinical use."
